### Pet API

### Get all pets (paginated)
GET {{host}}/api/v1/pets?page=0&size=20

### Get pet by ID
GET {{host}}/api/v1/pets/{{petId}}

### Create pet (DOG)
POST {{host}}/api/v1/pets
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Max",
  "species": "DOG",
  "breed": "Golden Retriever",
  "birthDate": "2022-03-15",
  "ownerId": "{{ownerId}}"
}

### Create pet (CAT)
POST {{host}}/api/v1/pets
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Whiskers",
  "species": "CAT",
  "breed": "Persian",
  "birthDate": "2021-07-20",
  "ownerId": "{{ownerId}}"
}

### Update pet
PUT {{host}}/api/v1/pets/{{petId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Buddy",
  "breed": "Labrador"
}

### Delete pet
DELETE {{host}}/api/v1/pets/{{petId}}

### Get visits by pet ID
GET {{host}}/api/v1/pets/{{petId}}/visits

### Get appointments by pet ID
GET {{host}}/api/v1/pets/{{petId}}/appointments

# Species enum values: DOG, CAT, BIRD, REPTILE, FISH, HAMSTER, RABBIT, OTHER
